802
00:50:31,294 --> 00:50:34,064
-Mr. Soma!
-What's up?

803
00:50:34,131 --> 00:50:38,101
Mr. Matsuki says he will take us to
a restaurant with cured meat.

804
00:50:38,168 --> 00:50:39,269
Matsuki?

805
00:50:39,336 --> 00:50:40,370
What?

806
00:50:41,538 --> 00:50:43,240
I was asking for a date.

807
00:50:44,875 --> 00:50:47,878
Is that the famous one near here?

808
00:50:48,512 --> 00:50:51,181
-Yes.
